Issue 6:


Regarding Master Data Creation:

JM Steel and Wheatland are currently not appearing in the final output due to join failure in the last step. This is likely caused by name mismatches between the Supplier field in the capacity CSV and Supplier_Name in the main dataset. This may need manual mapping or standardization (e.g., lowercase, trim, fuzzy match) to resolve.
